(790, 'GTag', '', 'Notifications Paragraph', '', 'Briefing Note 7 (May 2013 reissued RFP) is available for download.<br /><br /><b>Foreign exchange rate assumptions: </b> For purposes of the Third Bid Submission Phase, Bidders are required to use the following foreign exchange rate assumptions in preparing their Financial Model(s):<br /><span>USD: R9.86   EUR: R12.96   GBP: R14.91   CNY: R1.61  </span>RUB: R0.30  INR: R0.17 AUD: R9.09   JPY: R0.10   DKK: R1.74<br /><span><b><br /></b><b>Removal of Price caps in respect of Onshore Wind and Solar Photovoltaic Technologies:</b></span> For purposes of the Third Bid Submission Phase, the Department has decided to remove Price caps in respect of the Onshore Wind and Solar Photovoltaic Technologies.  Current registrations for these Technologies demonstrate that the Third Bid Submission Phase will be significantly oversubscribed.  The Department believes that market forces will prevail and result in the market determining the appropriate Price for these Technologies.  As such, the Department does not see a current need for Price caps for these Technologies and the RFP will be amended accordingly.  The Department reserves the right to reinstate Price caps for future Bid Submission Phases, if required.<br /><b><br />Price caps in respect of Concentrated Solar Power Technology: </b> For purposes of the Third Bid Submission Phase, in respect of Concentrated Solar Power Technology, the Department has decided to amend the RFP as follows:<br />1) The current cap in respect of <span>the Base Price will not be amended;<br /></span><span>2) The Peak Time as indicated in the RFP will be amended from the current 5:00pm to 8:59pm, to 4:30pm to 9:29pm; and<br /></span><span>3) The premium to be paid on the Base Price will be amended from the current 240%, to 270%.<br /></span><b><br />Price caps in respect of the remaining Technologies: </b>  For purposes of the Third Bid Submission Phase, the Price caps in respect of all other Technologies remain unchanged.<br /><br />A Briefing Note will be published next week to give effect to these amendments to the RFP.<br />', 'N;', 'file_manager', '', '*', '2013-02-17', '2013-07-19', 0, 767),
