(1043, 'GTag', '', 'Conference Info', NULL, '<table width="800" border="0" cellspacing="12" cellpadding="0" class="full items" style="margin-left:25px">\n<tbody><tr> <td width="56%"><h2>Helderfontein Estate &amp; Conference Venue</h2></td> <td width="42%">&nbsp;</td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style="padding-right:75px">Helderfontein is nestled in a scenic valley, along the banks of the Jukskei River, where you can get back to nature and take pleasure in the calmness &amp; tranquillity of the natural surroundings. The venue is ideally located a few kilometres north of Fourways, Sandton with easy access from Main Road, Lonehill</p></td> <td>Helderfontein Estate, Johannesburg<br> Thursday, 16 August 2012<br> Registration: 08h30<br> Conference commencement: 09h30<br> A networking session will follow the conference</td> </tr> <tr> <td><h2><img src="http://beanland.co.za/images/Helderfontein1small.jpg" width="300" height="200" alt="helderberg1"></h2></td> <td><img src="http://beanland.co.za/images/Helderfontein2small.jpg" width="300" height="200" alt="helderberg2"></td> </tr> <tr> <td><h2>Directions</h2></td> <td><p>&nbsp;</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p><strong>FROM THE AIRPORT</strong></p> <p style="padding-right:25px">Leave the Airport by the R24 Johannesburg Route<br> Continue on the R24 till you see the N1 Pretoria; take this off ramp<br> Continue on this highway till you N1 South; Roodepoort / Bloemfontein<br> Follow this signage till you see the Rivonia Off-ramp<br> Take this off ramp, at the end, turn right (stay in the left lane)<br> Turn right at the robots into the R564 Fourways (Witkoppen Road)<br> Follow this road till you reach the big intersection at Main / Witkoppen Road<br> Turn right into Main Road<br> Go through the Lonehill robots, over the river and up the hill.<br> On the left hand side, you will see a sign Helderfontein, turn left (Chattan Road)<br> Follow this road (you will cross over an intersection)<br> Go through the White Pillars into Helderfontein Estate and follow the road to the Security.</p></td> <td style="vertical-align:top"><p><strong>FROM SANDTON</strong></p> <p>When passing through under the N1 Highway, turn left into Witkoppen Road (R564)<br> Carry on straight for about 3 kilometers<br> Turn right into Main Road (R71)<br> About 1 kilometer you will pass over the Jukskei River<br> After 300 meters, turn left into Chattan Road<br> You will drive straight into Helderfontein Estate at the end of the road. Keep to your left.</p> <p><br> </p></td> </tr> <tr> <td style="padding-right:25px;vertical-align:top;padding-top:12px"><strong>FROM RANDBURG</strong><br> <br> If you are on Hendrik Verwoerd Drive keep straight until it becomes Main Road (R71)<br> Carry on straight, you will pass over the Jukskei River<br> After 300 meters, turn left into Chattan Road<br> You will drive straight into Helderfontein Estate at the end of the road. Keep to your left</td> <td style="padding-top:12px"><p><strong>FROM PRETORIA</strong><br> <br> Take Ben Schoeman to Johannesburg<br> Allandale Off-Ramp towards Kyalami<br>Go straight to a T Junction (AA Kyalami) in front of you, turn right<br> Turn left to a sign for Randburg M71 past Castle and go past Leeukop Prison on your left<br> On your right hand side there will be a sign posted HELDERFONTEIN ESTATE<br> Turn right into that road by the name of Chattan<br> Proceed straight with Chattan road until it becomes a gravel road<br> You will drive through white pillars written Helderfontein and keep to your left</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td style="padding-right:25px"><strong>FROM FOURWAYS MALL</strong><br> <br> Go on Witkoppen Road (R564) towards Sunninghill (Pineslopes Shopping Centre on your left &amp; Monte Casino on your right)<br> Turn left into Main Road (M71) towards Kyalami<br> Go straight over the traffic light at Lonehill<br> Pass over the Jukskei River<br> Turn left into Chattan Road (sign posted Helderfontein Estate)<br> Follow Chattan Road, it becomes gravel, keep straight into Helderfontein Estate</td> <td><p><strong>OR</strong><br> <br> If you are on William Nicol Drive (R511) keep on going straight, you will pass the<br> Fourways Crossing at the traffic light.<br> The next traffic light there is a board that shows Dainfern, pass this traffic light<br> Carry on straight with William Nicol<br> You will see a small shop on your left-hand side, then drive over a very small bridge<br> that goes over the Jukskei River, close to that bridge there is a road on your right<br> hand side called Erling Road. Turn right there<br> Turn left into Lynx</p> <p> At Nest Phuting School turn right into Carcal<br> At 3rd stop street turn right into McInnes<br> At 2nd stop street, turn right into Chattan Rd, which is a gravel Road<br> Carry on with this road, it goes straight to Helderfontein</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><strong>CO-ORDINATES</strong><br> <br> S 25.59.465''<br> E 28.01.315''</td> <td>&nbsp;</td> </tr> <tr> <td>&nbsp;</td> <td>&nbsp;</td> </tr> </tbody></table>', 'a:1:{s:3:"tag";s:3:"div";}', '', '', '*', '2013-02-17', '2012-12-12', 3, 350),
