eate jobs and uplift standard of living of the poorest of the poor.  We are targeting to design LED programmes that contribute towards the value chain of both the coal mining project as well as the power plant during construction, operation and post operation.  We have already engaged the Moqhka Local Municipality for collaboration on LED and Community Involvement on the mining side.  Target programmes include NGO operated Biomass plantations, ash beneficiation for brick manufacturing for low cost housing, industrial parks for support services to the mine and power plant, and training of local communities on scarce skills as may be identified by both Department of Labour and the project.  ', 'yes', 'no', 'yes', 'yes', 'no', 'no', 'no', '6', 'yes', 'yes', 'yes', '01/06/2014', 'no', '', 'yes', '', 'yes', '', 'no', 'Under negotiation', '6 months', 'See time table', 'See milestone chart', '6', 'corporate', '', 'no', 'no', 'no', '', '', '', '6', 'yes', 'draft', 'yes', 'Primary coal resouce for the project is at proven reserve designation at 10 million tons GTIS (Opencast mineable), and vast resource at inferred designation (120 million), further ongoing drilling is being undertaken to prove additional resource up to 24 million by October 2013 require to operate 300MW for a period of 20 years.  As this is brownfield (area of previous substantial mining for Vierfontein Power Plant), and existing reconnaissance drilling information, confidence level is high for proving all required resource up to 600MW.', 'Orkney, Free State, South Africa', '26', '46', '00', '27', '03', '19', 'no', '', 'no', 'no', '26/08/2013', 'yes', '13/01/2014', '31/03/2014', 'no', '', '', 'Water User Licence 12 months, Atmospheric Emission Licence 12 months, Generation Licence 6 months', '2.1', '26', '44''48', '78', '27', '02''57', '85', 'Jersey Distribution Substation', 'no', '', '', '', 'Various meeting have been held with Eskom and an initial power flow study conducted by Eskom indicates significant 