(91, 278, 'Mobesa Investments (Pty) Ltd.', '+27 79 493 5483', 'Mr. Ntsikelelo Matshatshe', '26 Villa Montigo ', '26', 'Gerber', 'Vorna Valley', 'Midrand', '1685', 'ntsiki.matshatshe@gmail.com', 'Coega 3200 CCGT Power Project', '1. Proposed 3,200 MW Closed Cycle Gas Turbine (CCGT) Power Plant for the Coega Development Corporation IDZ Zone.\r\n2. The Plant will be powered by natural Gas (LNG).\r\n3. Main cost drivers include cost of natural gas (25 year Contract to be entered into), electricity tariffs, exchange rate of the Rand, cost of labour and materials.\r\n4. The CDC has done a lot of work since Project inception including issuing EOI after Project Definition and Scoping. The Project is ready for Implementation. The outstanding Legislative and Regulatory processes must be completed, the required IPP License should be granted and the Project given the go ahead.\r\n', 'GasPlant', 'CCGT', 'LNG', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '3520', '800', '3200', '85', '0.75', 'Not Available', '>74%', '', '', '', 'Quater2', '2015', 'First Turbine commissioned 22 months after turn of soil', '22', 'baseload', '', '', '', 'yes', '', 'no', '', 'no', '', '75000', '25', '1.35', '', 'Unknown at this stage', 'yes', '', 'fastQ2-2013-24Month', '', '1.5', '22', 'Consortium to include Panda Energy, Aether Energy, Mobesa Investments and Private Business from Eastern Cape (BEE)', 'Panda Energy, USA', 'Mobesa Investments (Pty) Ltd.', 'Panda Energy, USA', 'Panda Energy has been in this business for 25 years and have constructed Power Plants in the United States of America, Africa, South America, Asia, China to name a few. Altogether, the company has developed, financed, constructed and operated over 9,000 megawatts of domestic and international generating capacity including the two largest gas fired, merchant power plants in the United States. Other Power Projects are being pursued in Namibia, Zimbabwe and Angola.                                                             ', '0', '0', '0',