(102, 288, 'mmt group', '0315357045', 'jabu madlala', 'first floor', '21 ', 'Aurora Drive', 'umhlanga', 'durban', '4301', 'ceo@mmtgroup.co.za', 'phezulunenatal energy', 'good day\r\n\r\nWe are an emerging BBEEE firm in energy.  We have projects in North Natal. We have been struggling to get electricity as we still use Solar energy.  Eskom has delayed the installation for a long time.  We wish to therefore register our intent to provide energy to the community and communities.\r\nWe have consulted and we believe in the sustainability as the community need energy/ electricity.\r\nWe have been talking to foreign large entities to partner with us and agreements are imminent.\r\nWe believe we will be able to connect to the grid soon.  we will scale up the generation capacity over time.  Our focus will be biomass\r\nWe have the land or rights to the land for over 18,000ha. \r\nWe believe we can begin commission within 18 months.  We believe this are should be prioritised by the department as it needs power energy.  We are ready and we are happy to provide details at an appropriate time to substantiate our proposal.\r\n\r\nOur partners, funding partners and the community are ready awaiting the department of energy decision to proceed with this initiative.  We are BBEEE and we are women owned, and working with the community in delivering this project.\r\n\r\nWe will submit a hard copy of the submission to support this electronic submission.\r\n\r\nCEO\r\nMMT GROUP\r\n\r\n', 'Thermal', 'BiomassCurrent', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '25', '10', '10', '75', '.40', 'inflation based', '', '', '', '', 'Quater3', '2014', '', '12', 'mid-merit', '12', '365', '20', 'no', '', 'no', '', 'no', '', '50', '20', '1.5', '', '7', 'yes', '', 'commitQ3-2013-Phased', '', '9', '6', 'mmt', '', 'mmt', 'emerasco', 'partner experience', '1000000', '2000000', '3000000', 'no', '', '', '', '', 30, 'local women owned company', 'no', 'no', 'no', 'no', 'no', '', 'no', '6', 'no', '', '', '', '',