(120, 317, 'SVA', '0127034016', 'HAO MIN', 'stand 112, ', '7', 'zone 15', 'Ga-rankuwa industrial', ' Pretoria', '0208', 'hhatt0411@hotmail.com', 'low temperature power generation ', 'Low temperature (industrial waste heat) power generation system\r\n\r\nA, OVERVIEW\r\n\r\nAll the products are classified into two categories:\r\n\r\nFirst?Power generation system by low temperature difference. \r\n\r\nMainly used in the working conditions that the temperature difference between heat source /cold source and the atmospheric environment temperature is more than 60? and less than 120?. The single machine capacity is 20-5000kw, and could be connected in parallel. The thermoelectric conversion efficiency is 10%-15%. \r\n\r\nSuch as the following working conditions:\r\n\r\n1. Condensate water with temperature ?85?and flow rate?35t/h?hot water in the process needed be cooled?thermal oil ?thermal material?The boiler continuous sewage ?the geothermal water and so on.\r\n2. Low temperature power generation by the solar photothermal, by the heat of exhaust gas condensate of the natural gas boiler(single capacity is over 10 tons), by the high temperature exhaust gas, by low pressure Exhaust steam ?flow rate is more than 2t/h ?whose temperature ?100?\r\n3. Power co-generation by temperature and pressure difference of the cold energy from LNG Gasification .\r\n4?Power generation by blast furnace slag water ,furnace cooling water, mill of the cooling water in the steel industry, and so on \r\n5?Power generation by cooling water in high temperature from large size marine engines\r\n\r\nSecond?Medium -high temperature ultra-efficient power generation system. \r\n\r\nMainly used in the working conditions that the heat source temperature is higher than 200?. The single machine capacity is 500-20000kw, and could be connected in parallel. The thermoelectric conversion efficiency is 35%-50%.Such as the following working conditions:\r\n\r\n1?Saturated steam with the pressure ?1.6MPa?Process material with the temperature ?200??Waste heat boiler high-temperature hot -water, medium-temperature hot-water in the solar heater.\r\n2?Power direct generation by primary energy source?natural gas?fuel oil?coal),biomass, nuclear fusion. The thermoelectric conversion efficiency is more than 40%.\r\n3?Marine AIP closed loop dynamic systems, taking the oxidation reaction of ethano liquid oxygen as heat source. It can replace the large size diesel engine. It has low noise, high efficiency, and long lifetime. And can also run continuously for a long time.\r\n\r\nB, ADVANTAGES\r\n\r\n\r\n• Can economically utilize any temperature above 190°F/88°C .\r\n• Closed loop system results in lower life cycle costs .\r\n• Proprietary supercritical design improves performance over standard subcritical by 10-15%.\r\n• Standard working fluid is non-flammable, safe and non-corrosive.\r\n• Condensers operate at above atmospheric pressure.\r\n• Systems don’t require demineralizers, blow-down systems or vacuum systems.\r\n• Designed for minimal operations and maintenance.\r\n• Low demand on space ,compared to other RE generation technologies.\r\n• Environment friendly, control emissions of carbon dioxide.\r\n• 24 hours interruptible power generation\r\n• Technology Registered in EU,can be widely adopted, eg. solar thermal, geothermal, biomass,\r\n\r\nC, Main cost Drivers\r\n\r\n1, Once off equipment investments\r\n2, Low maintanence cost, (require 4 times minor maintenance a year and one major service every three years) as it doesn''t require demineralizers\r\n', 'Cogeneration', 'Integrated', 'Recomission', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '2', '2', '2', '70', '0.65', '1.2', '', '', '', '', 'Quater3', '2020', 'The designed life time of the equipment is 20 years', '180', 'baseload', '', '', '', 'no', '', 'no', '', 'no', '', '15', '20', '0.85', '', '1.2', 'yes', '', 'commitQ3-2013-Phased', '', '2', '6', 'SVA', '', 'NONE', 'INESA', 'OVERSEAS PROJECTS ,XINJIANG CSP PROJECTS', '12000000', 