(133, 349, 'Itumeleng Molotsi/ Mpho Scott', '0715830300', 'Itumeleng Molotsi', 'Curadox House', '25', 'Autumn Street', 'Rivonia', 'Johannesburg', '2000', 'tumi@silvaplaite.co.za', 'Richardsbay Coal Fired Power Station', 'The Project for a 1200MW coal fired power station close to Richards Bay in KZN. The development team has secured land and sufficient low cost and low grade coal for the power station. Negotiations are complete to acquire the existing operating and licensed mining operation and coal reserve. Sufficient water is available close to the sites and the mine has a water use license which the power station can draw from.\r\n\r\nBy utilizing Circulating Fluidized Bed (CFB) technology we will be able to use high ash, low volatile coal efficiently with very low enviromental impact and to World Bank standards. The land has been negotiated with the Ingonyama Trust and Usuthu Traditional Council. Approvals on the land has been granted and three sites are being evaluated. Logistics will be minimized by placing the power station in close proximity to the mining operations. \r\n', 'Thermal', 'Coal', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1320', '330', '1200', '85', '0.75', '100%', '37.1', '', '', '', 'Quater1', '2019', '', '48', 'baseload', '11.2', '330', '24', 'yes', '', 'yes', 'DOE Peaker Power Station', 'no', '', '29.000', '20', '850.00', '', '100', 'yes', '', 'commitQ2-2015-Phased', '', '12', '48', 'Silvaplaite/Curadox', 'TBA', 'Silvaplaite/Curadox', 'TBA', 'Curadox shareholder involved as BEE shareholder in DOE Peaker. Mr. Mpho Scott and Mr. Koos Smit will also be directors in the project', '3000000.00', '3500000.00', '4000000.00', 'no', '', '', '', '', 51, 'The project has strong support from King Zwelithini and the 10% community structure will be negotiated with him and his council. It is possible that the King may take a direct interrest in the project', 'no', 'no', 'no', 'yes', 'no', 'no', 'no', '24', 'yes', 'yes', 'yes', '10/07/2019', 'no', '', 'yes', ''