(213, 371, 'Lotsha Energy', '0828753317', 'Mashudu Matlala', 'Ashwood Place Ground Floor ', '140', 'Western Service Road', 'Woodmead', 'Johannesburg', '2199', 'mashudu@manenzhegroup.co.za', 'Amersfoot CBM plant', 'There is authorised exploration of Coal Bed Methane in the Ermerlo Coal field. The propose project is to take the gas that is produced and feed it into a power plant to be developed on site. This will reduce the complexities associated with the transportation of this type of gas. The decisions to go ahead will generally be governed by the existence of a PPA, agreements between the explorers, developers and EPC companies. We  also expect to factor in the time required to get the associated permits and licences.', 'GasPlant', 'CCGT', 'NaturalGas', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '200', '50', '100', '50', '50', '1.3', '0.5', '', '', '', 'Quater4', '2016', 'Pending Acquisition of permits and generation licence', '18', 'mid-merit', '11', '330', '24', 'no', '', 'no', '', 'no', '', '2000', '20', '900', '', '1.3', 'yes', '', 'commitQ3-2013-Phased', 'Assuming that is Q3/4 2014', '12', '24', 'Lotsha Energy', 'TBC', 'Lotsha Energy', 'TBC', 'We are a registered IPPP under the DOE programme, developing PV power plants.', '0', '0', '0', 'no', '', '', '', '', 30, 'Yes we will register a trust to the benefit of the local community.', 'no', 'no', 'no', 'no', '', '', '', '6', 'no', 'no', 'no', '', 'no', '', 'yes', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '6', 'project', '', 'yes', 'no', 'no', '', '', '', '6', '', 'none', 'no', 'Yes, it is public knowledge that companies like Kinetiko are exploring the Ermelo coal fields area and have found gas up to 2.4 tcf which is capable of generating up to 600MW.  .', 'Ermelo, Amersfoort area', '27', '00', '28', '28', '52', '16', 'no', '', 'no', 'no', '', 'no', '', '', 'no', '', '', 'Generation Licence', '10', '27', '00', '28', '29', '52', '16', 'Ermelo SuB', 'no', '', '', '', 'None', 'TBC', 'TBC', '6', 'TBC', '30-40', '600', '30.00', 'Invol